OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA murky start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and low cloud. Some of the rain
OL,7,Fstill heavy in places at first,
OL,8,Fhowever gradually becoming lighter and
OL,9,Fmore patchy through the day. Staying
OL,10,Fcloudy and rather cool, with a
OL,11,Fgenerally light breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome cloud breaks may develop
OL,14,Ffrom the north, and turning chilly
OL,15,Fwhere these occur. Otherwise, largely
OL,16,Fcloudy, with hill fog patches and the
OL,17,Fodd spot of drizzle. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
