OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,6,Ffrom the north and mostly dry,
OL,7,Falthough isolated showers are still
OL,8,Fpossible. Winds remaining generally
OL,9,Flight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,13,Fshowers each day, although perhaps
OL,14,Fmore likely on Tuesday. Turning
OL,15,Fcooler, with overnight rural frost
OL,16,Fpossible in sheltered spots. Winds
OL,17,Fmostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
